    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入QQ交流群：346242365</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款第一人称快节奏射击游戏，玩家可以利用完全可破坏的环境，例如摧毁墙壁、家具和障碍物，制定战术策略，形成自己的战斗风格，击败从虚拟游戏世界入侵现实的像素怪物。在此基础上，我们融合了3D弹幕射击和肉鸽关卡机制，皆在为玩家带来爽快、解压、发泄式的战斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关键特性</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >破坏 - 场景中所有物体均可被破坏，包括地板，甚至可以将整个关卡完全消除</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爆炸 ​- 独特的3D像素爆炸效果，爽快的战斗、尽情的破坏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义“职业” - 自由组合枪械、技能、道具，找出适合自己的搭配</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摧毁怪物 - 可以像破坏场景一样摧毁怪物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态关卡 - 环境破坏机制带来了更多战术体验和玩法</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143510/extras/ae313e4ba47f5bbdf5bd5a177ce20dee.poster.avif?t=1768444442\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143510/extras/ae313e4ba47f5bbdf5bd5a177ce20dee.webm?t=1768444442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143510/extras/ae313e4ba47f5bbdf5bd5a177ce20dee.mp4?t=1768444442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143510/extras/bb4c8b589da0aad0f6d97080c2b569c1.poster.avif?t=1768444442\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143510/extras/bb4c8b589da0aad0f6d97080c2b569c1.webm?t=1768444442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143510/extras/bb4c8b589da0aad0f6d97080c2b569c1.mp4?t=1768444442\" type=\"video/mp4\"